{"tid":1001764,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【iPhone減價】救全球銷量　Tim Cook 承認太貴影響銷情","createTime":"2019-01-30T11:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T12:09:48.000Z","uid":18296,"like":50,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"67981f708257519c6afb7715957d79941876a57b","tid":1001764,"uid":18296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook 在路透社的一個專訪中承認，iPhone 收入按年下跌 15％ 的其中一個原因，是全球匯率變動影響到 iPhone 在部份國家地區的價格一直高企。他表示將在美國以外多個地區減價以令 iPhone 的銷量復甦。<br />\n<br />\n在早前發表的財政報告當中，iPhone 整體收入下跌 15％，而大中華地區的銷量更按年下跌 26.7%。Apple CEO 庫克（Tim Cook）在訪問中指出 3 個原因令到 iPhone 整體收入下跌。第一是匯率變動，Apple 在美國推出 iPhone XS 時價格與上一代 iPhone X 相同，iPhone XS Max 則較貴 100 美元，另一方面 iPhone XR 的價格則在 iPhone XS 與 iPhone 8 之間。在美國這個價格設定並無不妥，但美元持續高企令到全球大部份國家地區的新款 iPhone 售價比對上一代高出更多，例如土耳其在 10－12月期間的收入按年下跌 7 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n對此 Tim Cook 表示，他們會在 1 月開始對於微經濟受影響的國家地區，展開各種價格適正化的計畫，由 Apple 吸收部份匯價變動的影響。新價格將會更接近以往新機種發售時的價格。而另一方面亦會推出如舊機換新機優惠，以及分期付款的方式刺激銷量。<br />\n<br />\n而 Tim Cook 提到第二個影響 iPhone 收入的原因，是電訊商補助金的下跌，以日本為例，以往顧客購買 iPhone 電訊商都會投入大量補助金，但在當地政府的新政策之下，補助金額受到限制。第三就是 Apple 提供的電池更換計劃，令到顧客使用同一部 iPhone 的時間比以前更長。然而 Tim Cook 堅持推出電池更換計劃對用戶來說是一個正確的決定。<br />\n<br />\nTim Cook 表示，在以上眾多不利因素之下，整體 Apple 裝置的數字由 2018 年 1 月末的 13 億部，增加至 2018 年末的 14 億部。<br />\n<br />\nfrom <a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/01/30/timcookiphonechina/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2Ftimcookiphonechina%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=58e45131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/01/30/timcookiphonechina/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"630e95f3a7f49c9c8813d7a16b703e22bf2779b4","tid":1001764,"uid":94828,"like":82,"dislike":1,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"上年加到萬五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e7dc4763caa4230ebe4931e6454e84b51bdbe2","tid":1001764,"uid":105614,"like":229,"dislike":1,"score":228,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"繼續加啦 咁撚把炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c2b7f8da72ae5241826a0295976e882155e551","tid":1001764,"uid":50744,"like":215,"dislike":1,"score":214,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"太平喇<br />\n三萬一部我都買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302cfedc7e506ef58dc7cccdeea0b6b8895cb1dd","tid":1001764,"uid":122472,"like":122,"dislike":2,"score":120,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"第三就是 Apple 提供的電池更換計劃，令到顧客使用同一部 iPhone 的時間比以前更長。"},{"pid":"48528a94a5176e9efe021aae7d8b25c0103dd337","tid":1001764,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"今年有大改變. <br />\n設計上應該會大改 搶番班 6千蚊客."},{"pid":"b36d51af05cb5e608d514cf82b4ecd9acf698dd7","tid":1001764,"uid":20664,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"quote":{"pid":"302cfedc7e506ef58dc7cccdeea0b6b8895cb1dd","tid":1001764,"uid":122472,"like":122,"dislike":2,"score":120,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:52:56.000Z","msg":"第三就是 Apple 提供的電池更換計劃，令到顧客使用同一部 iPhone 的時間比以前更長。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:55:09.000Z","msg":"唔推呢啲留唔到人用iOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace54ee75fecb7c05160d82715e5bc2fad32b05a","tid":1001764,"uid":20664,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"48528a94a5176e9efe021aae7d8b25c0103dd337","tid":1001764,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"今年有大改變. <br />\n設計上應該會大改 搶番班 6千蚊客."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"iPhone已經係luxury product<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f647d73a1df5e15026bd824242e5ecdb5d17fe5","tid":1001764,"uid":21052,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"環保撚快d抵制iPhone啦 製造埋xr呢d咁既膠機 電子垃圾"},{"pid":"696506b7d030b0a9b5e8ea67a84b02e7c058fed7","tid":10017